message:
Dialogue-based language learning environment. (#72)

* Dialogue-based language learning environment.
In this environment, the teacher verbally interacts with the learner
about randomly selected object classes, and provides sentence feedback
as well as reward feedback according to learner's response.
This provides an environment for grounded language learning through
dialogue interactions.
